
***** List of basic commands *****

Command                            Description
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
cast <spell> (<arg1>) (<arg2>)     Cast a spell
* <message> or :<emote>            Use the guild chat line
renew                              renew your magesoul and restore from save
charge <amount>                    add spell points to your soul
spells                             list learned spells
teach <who> <spell>                try to teach someone a spell
recruit <who>                      only the guild master may recruit members
mon/itor                           toggle the guild monitor
ansi (<on/off>)                    (de)activate ansi sequences
emote <what>                       emote a string
info (<topic>)                     display guild help messages

Note: Arguments in parentheses are optional.

Try typing "info list" and "info <spell>."

Have fun!

--Bastian
